  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2>Mila Ristevski is an experienced journalist who has been investigating disappearances in the city for many years. Recently, she managed to find an important clue that led her to the old estate. She decides to reveal the secrets of this house, but on the way to the truth, Mila will face real evil.<br><br>An old house is full of dark secrets, and every corner can hide danger or valuable information. You have to be careful, because any careless step can be fatal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/57b9bae3f3f49216036cd3b3c4a414ca.poster.avif?t=1721754656\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/57b9bae3f3f49216036cd3b3c4a414ca.webm?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/57b9bae3f3f49216036cd3b3c4a414ca.mp4?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goal:</h2>Your task is to explore the environment, solve puzzles and uncover secrets to survive. Each room may contain clues or traps, so carefully search all the nooks and crannies and use your logic and wits to unravel the secrets of the old estate. Your goal is not only to uncover the truth, but also to get out of there alive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/04e9a4d23b38eaaa50893788d5611ea6.poster.avif?t=1721754656\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/04e9a4d23b38eaaa50893788d5611ea6.webm?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/04e9a4d23b38eaaa50893788d5611ea6.mp4?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/f955508e35978bd14c18cf6136cce871.poster.avif?t=1721754656\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/f955508e35978bd14c18cf6136cce871.webm?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/f955508e35978bd14c18cf6136cce871.mp4?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The minimum number of hints will complicate the process, so you need to be as attentive and clever as possible.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/3f2a204502cf5663333660bf96734388.poster.avif?t=1721754656\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/3f2a204502cf5663333660bf96734388.webm?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/3f2a204502cf5663333660bf96734388.mp4?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be careful:</h2>Each action must be performed carefully, as you can be attacked at any moment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/a2d36068797bb85fdf79b59fc1a5ca98.poster.avif?t=1721754656\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/a2d36068797bb85fdf79b59fc1a5ca98.webm?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856490/extras/a2d36068797bb85fdf79b59fc1a5ca98.mp4?t=1721754656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Darkness lurks at every turn and your decisions affect the outcome of this deadly game. Will you be able to cope with this terrifying ordeal? Your wits and courage will be your only allies in the fight against the evil that lurks in the shadows. Survival depends on your ability to solve mysteries and evade the dangers that lie in wait at every turn. Are you ready to take on this challenge?",
